Sentencas: Titanium, Ti-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-delta (x = 0.1-0.5) perovskite-structured ceramics were synthesized via solution combustion.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The structural, morphological, and electrochemical behaviors of the as-synthesized materials were investigated to determine the applicability of SrFe1-xTixO3-delta as a cobalt-free cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction analysis confirmed the formation of a single-phase cubic perovskite structure.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The unit volume of this perovskite structure increased as the amount of Ti dopant increased.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: Morphological analysis revealed that the porosity of the SrFe1-xTixO3-delta perovskite cathode film was inversely proportional to the amount of Ti dopant.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The cathode SrFe0.9Ti0.1O3-delta film exhibited a high porosity of 24.74 +/- 0.52%, a low but acceptable hardness value of 0.70 +/- 0.01 GPa and an area specific resistance of 0.57 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: These results suggested that cobalt-free SrFe1-xTixO3-delta cathode was still not good enough to be compared with the existing cobalt-containing cathode such as lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: But, the results obtained from this work can be considered as a major turning point as the literature works on SrFe1-xTixO3-delta cathode showed excellence electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The contradict result between the present and past studies proved that the use of SrFe1-xTixO3-delta cathode is worthy of being studied into details to confirm its capability.
Titulo: Structural, morphological, and electrochemical behavior of titanium-doped SrFe1-xTixO3-δ (x=0.1-0.5) perovskite as a cobalt-free solid oxide fuel cell cathode
